{"tid":918231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8歲女孩北京開車上路拍抖音 其父被罰2千吊銷駕照","createTime":"2018-11-27T04:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T08:12:45.000Z","uid":75969,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"40fab4e898cd02355907c619b06de685e6c338f5","tid":918231,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181127/_2018112710315918033.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181127%2F_2018112710315918033.jpg&h=98b447cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，一則「未滿10歲女孩在北京開車上路」的影片在網絡上流傳。影片中，一位女童操控軚盤駕駛私家車在公路上行駛。而這段影片最早是由女孩父親在抖音上發佈的。除此之外，他還通過朋友圈發布炫耀。11月21日上午，此影片在網上多處轉發，網民紛紛指責這位家長的做法。而在當事人的抖音賬號上，該視頻隨即被刪除。當事男子由於讓8歲的女兒違規駕駛汽車，將面臨2000元罰款，並處以吊銷駕駛執照處罰。<br />\n<br />\n就在影片熱傳的當天，北京警方立即展開調查工作，鎖定了當事人。11月21日下午，喬某某（男，40歲，戶籍天津）被依法傳喚到公安機關，並如實承認了自己的違法行為。據喬某某講述，大概今年9月中旬幫朋友搬家，駕車途中，孩子覺得好玩說讓她開一會，於是就讓8歲女兒揸軚盤駕駛，他在後面保護着，並錄了一段影片。現在他非常後悔，已經認識到這種行為給自己、家人、其他駕駛者、路人帶來的潛在危害，今後一定會遵守交通法規。喬某某將面臨2000元罰款，並處吊銷駕駛執照處罰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181127/_2018112710320075980.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181127%2F_2018112710320075980.jpg&h=5e991323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">喬某某將面臨2000元罰款，並處吊銷駕駛執照處罰。（網圖）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/874102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F874102&d=WdnXGFwYqTUALziYLj88ri7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=cadaa4fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F874102&h=54b8788d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/874102</a>"},{"pid":"b2cf27fdc8af9c30a74d454799f89f9d1b52a46f","tid":918231,"uid":29606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:00:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e1b9406b42b557f7adf30904b44e0ce3ada868d","tid":918231,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:09:49.000Z","msg":"個罪咁輕<br />\n試下香港丫，監都有得坐。"},{"pid":"271e5b64d65f95288e6e7bb7820d6314335d145b","tid":918231,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e1b9406b42b557f7adf30904b44e0ce3ada868d","tid":918231,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:09:49.000Z","msg":"個罪咁輕<br />\n試下香港丫，監都有得坐。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:12:45.000Z","msg":"好似香港試過"}]}